overview:
Bytewalls is a small business located in Austin, TX that does small scale web design and development.

Owned and operated by a high school student, Bytewalls is more dedicated to customer service than the newest features. They are currently using ModX and WordPress as their primary CMS which they implement on all websites they create.

Looking for expansion oppurtunities they are currently venturing into the Mobile Phone development market, their adventures into mobile apps is well documented on their very open transparent blog.
